{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.440", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.680", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als die Pflegeversicherung in den 1990er-Jahren eingef\u00fchrt wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "war ich bei den Jungen Liberalen politisch engagiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.200", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir waren entsetzt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.640", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht \u00fcber die Pflegeversicherung an sich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Einf\u00fchrung war ein richtiger und wichtiger Schritt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.400", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir waren entsetzt \u00fcber ein weiteres soziales Sicherungssystem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei dem Junge f\u00fcr Alte zahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dies, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl man genau wusste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.600", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass im Zuge des demografischen Wandels immer weniger Junge f\u00fcr immer mehr Alte w\u00fcrden zahlen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.120", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier wurde ein ungedeckter Scheck auf die junge Generation ausgestellt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damals als Junge Liberale hielt ich das f\u00fcr einen Fehler. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und wir Freie Demokraten wollen diesen Fehler nicht verschlimmern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir dieses System auch noch zu einer Vollversicherung ausbauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.920", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Klug und weitsichtig w\u00e4re es gewesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schon damals ein System einzuf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sich auf R\u00fccklagen st\u00fctzt und so auf nachfolgende Generationen R\u00fccksicht nimmt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.360", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen von den Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.320", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es hier eine durchgreifende politische Initiative der Bundesregierung geben sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.120", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann doch die, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.200", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere sozialen Sicherungssysteme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.760", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch die Pflegeversicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.640", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich generationengerecht anzulegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.000", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nachhaltigkeit gilt doch nicht nur f\u00fcr unsere Umwelt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch f\u00fcr unsere Finanzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.920", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis zum Jahr\u00a02030 soll die Zahl zu Pflegender auf 3,5\u00a0Millionen anwachsen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders rasant wird die Zahl der Pflegef\u00e4lle bei Hochbetagten steigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie soll all das finanziert werden? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne mehr Eigenverantwortung wird es aus Sicht der Freien Demokraten nicht gehen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um auch gerade die Menschen weiterhin auffangen zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.480", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich aus eigener Kraft nicht helfen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.520", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke da vor allem an Langzeitarbeitslose, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alleinerziehende und Erwerbsgeminderte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.080", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.640", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vieles liegt bei der Pflege im Argen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen den Pflegenotstand in Deutschland dringend beseitigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.360", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen h\u00e4nderingend mehr Pflegekr\u00e4fte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.800", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber woher sollen diese Pflegekr\u00e4fte kommen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.200", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Pflegeausbildung ist auf halber Strecke liegen geblieben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Finanzierung ist nicht gekl\u00e4rt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.800", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da gebe ich Ihnen Recht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.520", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist ein Unding, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Eigenanteil in Pflegeheimen als Ausbildungsumlage in der Altenpflege dient. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.080", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch deshalb fordern wir die Bundesregierung auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.480", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich eine Regelung zur Finanzierung der Pflegeausbildung aus Steuermitteln vorzulegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.320", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die der Bund geradesteht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.360", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt ein Wort zu den privaten Anbietern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.200", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie wieder einmal verteufeln\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.000", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu Unrecht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ich finde;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.880", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn in Zeiten von Pflegenotstand brauchen wir nicht weniger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.360", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern mehr privates Engagement in der Pflege."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.880", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie sonst wollen wir den steigenden Bedarf an Pflegepl\u00e4tzen decken? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist nichts Unanst\u00e4ndiges, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.520", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch in der Pflege gewinnorientiert zu arbeiten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.520", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pflegekr\u00e4fte sollen angemessen bezahlt werden und bessere Arbeitsbedingungen erhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.120", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit der Beruf attraktiver wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.160", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie soll man das denn sonst schaffen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.280", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn es Missst\u00e4nde gibt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Missst\u00e4nde sind nat\u00fcrlich unertr\u00e4glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.920", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch bei Privaten\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.640", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann geh\u00f6ren doch die Missst\u00e4nde abgeschafft und nicht die privaten Einrichtungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.280", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "L\u00f6sen Sie sich doch endlich von der irrigen Vorstellung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.680", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Staat alles besser kann!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.520", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unser Ziel muss es sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Finanzierung der Pflegekosten endlich so zu gestalten,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.560", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie auch f\u00fcr k\u00fcnftige Generationen tragf\u00e4hig sein wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.600", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.080", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schaffen wir schnell Klarheit bei der Finanzierung der Pflegeausbildung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.240", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verbessern wir die Arbeitsbedingungen in der Pflege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.160", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sorgen wir daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.960", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in der Pflege jetzt und in der Zukunft nicht nur soziale Gerechtigkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.840", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch Generationengerechtigkeit herrscht!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.840", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Fraktion B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen hat die Kollegin Kordula Schulz-Asche das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}